Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.59,0:45:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,几天後
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.00,0:45:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼穿這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.00,0:45:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我在洗澡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.61,0:45:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,來的不是时候我怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.88,0:45:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,明明這么久没见了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.95,0:45:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,姐也一起泡吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.02,0:45:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.35,0:46:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,進去慢慢談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.90,0:46:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,姐的身材真好
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.04,0:46:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,有在鍛鍊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.12,0:46:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不是男人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.65,0:46:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不是有男友嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.06,0:46:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.60,0:46:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真羨慕妳
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.74,0:46:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你也有老公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.01,0:46:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可是他出差了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.15,0:47:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那妳就跟去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.82,0:47:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.69,0:47:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那就麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.56,0:47:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我的兒子和明
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.77,0:47:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.25,0:47:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,媽不在時要听阿姨的話唷
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.32,0:47:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.52,0:47:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.80,0:47:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.07,0:47:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.80,0:48:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,別給人家添麻煩唷
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.21,0:48:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.28,0:48:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.69,0:48:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨会照顧你的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.76,0:48:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,也会煮飯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.30,0:48:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.17,0:48:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,反抗期嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.31,0:48:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,還是被女友甩了?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.05,0:48:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直單身
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.32,0:48:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.06,0:48:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会一直交不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.34,0:49:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.24,0:49:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也不出門?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.84,0:49:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.72,0:49:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,会后悔的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.46,0:49:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,老了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.13,0:50:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真的沒女友？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.80,0:50:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没有也沒差
