Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.64,0:50:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,沒差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.93,0:51:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,原来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.66,0:51:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,经验不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.30,0:51:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,妳干啥啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.10,0:51:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,幫你擦背啊
